rComments: Professor Faller is one of the best professors at Uottawa. His pre-recorded lectures were very informative and fun to listen to. The textbook was definitely useful and can help with the paper assignment. Professor Faller was always available over email and he also held a zoom meeting once a week for any questions you may have.

He conveys the material really well and he's available outside class for questions about the presentation, weekly assignments or the written paper. The presentation, weekly assignments and written paper require a lot of effort but they're doable. You need to attend each class because participation is graded.
